        "html": "<p><em><u><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=In%20Florida%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20Republican%20lawmakers%20are%20using%20faulty%20research%20to%20deny%20young%20people%20access%20to%20vital%20gender-affirming%20care%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levernews.com%2Fjunk-science-is-being-used-to-attack-trans-youth%2F%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dlink%26utm_campaign%3Dtw-prefill\">Click to share on Twitter</a></strong></u></em></p>"
      },
